{
  "stem": "4830.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We could hardly hear each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So four more shots.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said that I am right, and we managed to shoot them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we managed to cause tremendous damage in the Fifth District headquarter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We lost eight to nine people in [INAUDIBLE], but I don't how many-- their losses were over 100.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we managed to get to this boy, whom we can-- could not take out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Actually, his order was either take him out or kill him, if we cannot take him out out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If he's so seriously injured, he was dead.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they tortured him to death.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he evidently didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we left him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We came out.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the next day, there were still papers published.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They said that Russian commandos attacked the Fifth District headquarter.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But they were repelled with heavy losses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was a good deal of satisfaction to know that it wasn't three Russians commandos.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And nobody repelled us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Fortunately, they were all sleeping or drunk.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So we managed to break through them and we had about 35 hand grenades.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We used most of them in throwing to their sleeping quarters.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And it was a very satisfactory event.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And that was the only one in which I participated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And this was not even known to members of the house-- that we went through this.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Most of them did not know that we provided a final defense for them.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Because we were not able to speak.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And one of the reasons why I wanted to say this because I think this should be remembered.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "That was sometimes an opportunity to-- to fight back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And when it came, we used this opportunity.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after this, we still had at least 12, 14 days to survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
